									<ul class="bullets">
										<li><strong>Analyzing</strong> data sent to and from your devices for risks, threats, vulnerabilities, suspicious activity, and attacks;</li>
										<li><strong>Assessing</strong> the reputation of the sending and receiving device to see whether access should be allowed; and</li>
										<li><strong>Adapting</strong> responses to new threats based on intelligence from your device and our global network.</li>
									</ul>
