	<!-- Slide 5 Marginalia-->
								<div class="marginalia right baby">
						  		        <p>A bot is software that automatically does things when triggered to do so. Its name comes from "robot."</p>
									<p>A virus is software that spreads from one computer or device usually without the users permission. Like viruses in humans, viruses in computers or devices affect functionality. A virus can be a bot (and visa versa).</p>
									<p>Malware is software that can harm you or your computer or device.</p>

								</div>
	<!-- End Slide 5 Marginalia-->

